{"tid":472217,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊斥李飛不應將港獨自決思潮歸咎23條未立法","createTime":"2017-11-18T04:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T05:02:00.000Z","uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9271dbb652a4c516a486dfac6ec81404a0943fab","tid":472217,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:25:10.000Z","msg":"基本法委員會主任李飛日前在一個研討會上，指港府一直未為《基本法》23條立法，其不良影響有目共睹。行政會議成員、民主思路召集人湯家驊批評李飛的言論，對港人不公平。湯指出，即使港府2003年成功為23條立法，亦阻止不到今日發生的事，因現時香港的問題是因社會情緒而引發，並非用刑法就可避免或糾正，認為港府應多做立法以外的工作，而非單靠23條立法阻嚇。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊在商台節目表示，李飛的發言主要讓港人思考在一個兩制下，如何面對一國，以及糾正有港人誤以為《基本法》是源於《中英聯合聲明》。湯家驊又說，李飛提到中央擁有全面管治權，但無暗示中央的全面管治權會令港府的管治權被替代或削弱。<br />\n<br />\n湯續指，現時中央政府不會輕易讓香港普選特首，但認為政改不只是普選，亦可有其他改革，例如修改立法會選舉的比例代表制。"},{"pid":"bdb3b295e39561327b65049ec665484f008178ee","tid":472217,"uid":110832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:28:16.000Z","msg":"湯家驊幾時死"},{"pid":"6a0beaedd9bb25a23b331d0a3af62a2ac1dc01ae","tid":472217,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:29:26.000Z","msg":"小罵大幫忙<br />\n11驊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3a3873729a563f018733e6d6dd98a393873772","tid":472217,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs